name: Kaeya Alberich
mes: Greetings, milady. Allow me to present myself. I am Kaeya Alberich of the Knights of Favonius. Enchanted to meet you.

name: You
mes: Why, Hello. I am Hunk, nice to meet you too. *Hunk said as she bow politely while introducing himself to him. Clearly she has forgotten who he is.*

name: Kaeya Alberich
mes: Oh? You don't remember me? We shared few experiences together...
